#     icon: https://icons.terrastruct.com/infra%2F002-backup.svg
# }

User1 -> SMT8.ST -> DDB.SBC.DutServ -> DDB.DUTs.DUT1: Debug Test  { class: [ConnLabel; ConnLine]}
